<section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I am a dedicated educator with a passion for fostering growth in students. I teach bilingual U.S. History and ESL, lead a guitar club at school, and have extensive experience tutoring. Beyond the classroom, I am a filmmaker who has presented work at national conferences and an aspiring writer documenting my journey as an immigrant. My goal is to inspire creativity and learning in every facet of life.</p>
